{"tid":1332045,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文革到了]團體請願要求教育局懲處旺角示威中涉犯法教師","createTime":"2019-07-19T07:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T07:10:44.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe419cb8f52104d13c9bc32092a7e5baf02fdad","tid":1332045,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"民間團體「新年代」一批代表由金鐘遊行至政府總部，要求教育局盡快懲處在旺角示威涉嫌犯法的老師，教育局派人接收請願信。<br />\n<br />\n「新年代」副召集人黄勵賢說，近日多名老師參與遊行示威，當中有老師涉嫌作出違法行為，她認為教育局必須作出嚴懲，代表稍後將到旺角教協示威。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1469235_1_20190719150006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1469235_1_20190719150006.jpg&h=0098fab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469235-20190719.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469235-20190719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV%2FolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=9b09e61e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469235-20190719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e67f189e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469235-20190719.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我提下班新移民，一日未判，佢都係無罪之身，只係疑犯，何況有現場片段證實當時位女教師只係調解雙方，狗狗亂咬</span></strong>"}]}